---
title: Teriyaki Glazed Salmon with broccoli and garlic rice
description: Fans of fish are sure to love this nutritious yet delicious Asian-inspired recipe. Even better, the whole thing comes together in less than 30 minutes. That just means you've got more time to enjoy the appealing umami flavour of this tangy teriyaki dish.
